DB: COME BACK DRILL X 2(10 YDS BACK PEDAL, REGRESO 5 DIAGONAL ABAJO 45 GRADOS L/R    POST CORNER DRILL X 2 ( BACK PEDAL 10 YDS & 45 SPRINT TERMINAR EN 20YDS.
